Welcome into this file :)

This here is the port of NeHe's Lesson 21 to Linux/SDL
It should also work in Beos, Windoze and MacOS
If you're interested in running it on these platforms, go to

http://www.libsdl.org/Xmingw32/index.html

This port also has one improvement over the original version:
Background music!

The music was created by the Lizard King
His webpage can be found at http://www.itv.se/~a1055/



